dc_title_s: West Indies, Cuba--south coast, Jucaro to Cayos Gitanos (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency Hydrographic/Topographic Center. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "From Cuban charts to 1976." "Soundings in meters." Includes compilation diagram and tidal information. Map no.27201. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
